        "text": "In fact it seems to me that technology like blockchains made people realise that it is about *trust* how to trust other people. Its very interesting how technology in that sense became a kind of culture\/society media for discussing values and norms ( transparency vs. privacy, trust vs trustless) which can be already seen here: <https:\/\/kernel.community\/en\/learn\/module-0\/trust\/>",
